  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to aspirate immature oocytes from antral follicles and mature the
      oocytes in vitro. These mature oocytes will serve for fertilization and the creation of
      embryos which will be replace in the uterus as performed during normal IVF.We will record the
      efficacy and safety of this procedure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
